data.description: Welcoming to 67411 Rio Madre Dr. take a look at this spacious 2076 sqft homein Rio Vista Verano. Featuring elegant floors, an abundance of natural light, an innovative Kitchen Island that serves as the perfect gathering place for family and friends. The open plan layout creates a comfortable, inviting atmosphere, making this delightful residence a perfect choice for those seeking a well-designed and enjoyable living experience. Featuring four comfortable bedrooms, three and a half well-appointed bathrooms, a spacious layout.Discover the allure of a stylish kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, Pantry, light countertops and dark brown cabinets that exude a sophisticated, yet warm, ambiance. The dining area, adorned with stunning stone countertops, adds a touch of elegance, while the separate dining area provides a perfect space for more intimate gatherings and special occasions.This delightful property features a detached garage, providing added convenience. The spacious blank backyard is ideal for you to design your  back yard. Don't miss out on the chance to own this dream home with a unique combination of amenities.
